summary: Fixes Dawnbreaker so that it benefits from Ebony Smithing.
descriptionHtml:
.:Description:.
This was a quick mod I put together for a friend and he recommended that I upload it so here we go. What this does is let Dawnbreaker benefit from Ebony Smithing....so you don\'t have to fortify blacksmithing just to temper it to max.

If you like it then please make sure to endorse so that others may also enjoy it.

.:Version History:.
1.0 - Dawnbreaker benefits from ebony smithing
